---
const reveal = 'opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition duration-700 ease-out';
---

<section
  id="nosotros"
  class="mt-8 grid gap-8 border-t border-black/6 py-12 sm:mt-10 sm:py-14 md:justify-items-center md:gap-9 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(260px,0.78fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] xl:items-center xl:justify-items-stretch xl:gap-12 xl:py-20 2xl:gap-16"
>
  <div data-reveal class={`${reveal} order-2 mx-auto w-full max-w-[24rem] overflow-hidden rounded-[1.85rem] shadow-[0_22px_45px_rgba(15,23,42,0.12)] sm:max-w-[26rem] sm:rounded-[2.2rem] md:max-w-[25rem] xl:order-1 xl:max-w-[30rem] 2xl:max-w-[32rem]`}>
    <img
      src="/WhatsApp Image 2026-03-21 at 6.06.45 PM (1).jpeg"
      alt="Vehiculo atendido en NASA Auto Lab"
      class="aspect-[1.28/1] h-full w-full object-cover object-[center_40%] sm:aspect-[1.18/1] md:aspect-[1.16/1] xl:aspect-[0.98/1] xl:object-[center_42%]"
    />
  </div>

  <div data-reveal style="transition-delay:120ms" class={`${reveal} order-1 md:mx-auto md:flex md:max-w-[40rem] md:flex-col md:items-center md:text-center xl:order-2 xl:mx-0 xl:block xl:max-w-none xl:items-stretch xl:text-left`}>
    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#fff2f3] px-4 py-2 text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-nasa-accent sm:text-[0.72rem] sm:tracking-[0.18em]">
      <svg class="size-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 12h4l2-5 4 10 2-5h6" />
        <path d="M18 5v4M16 7h4" />
      </svg>
      Nosotros
    </span>

    <h2 class="mt-7 mb-0 max-w-[12ch] font-display text-[clamp(2.05rem,8.8vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1.02] font-bold tracking-[-0.06em] text-nasa-text md:mx-auto xl:mx-0">
      Pasion por el rendimiento y la precision mecanica
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-5 max-w-[40rem] text-[0.96rem] leading-[1.72] text-slate-500 sm:mt-7 sm:text-[1.04rem] sm:leading-[1.7] md:mx-auto md:text-[1.08rem] xl:mx-0 xl:text-[1.24rem]">
      En nuestro Laboratorio Automotriz, entendemos que tu vehiculo es una maquina de precision. Desde NASA Auto Lab buscamos la mejora constante para brindar un servicio profesional y de calidad, ideal para el maximo desempeno de tu auto.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:mt-9 md:w-full md:max-w-[40rem] md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-6 xl:mt-10 xl:max-w-none xl:gap-8">
      <article class="rounded-[2rem] bg-[#fffafb] p-5 sm:p-6">
        <span class="mb-5 grid size-12 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[#fff0f1] text-nasa-accent">
          <svg class="size-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.05em] text-nasa-text sm:text-[1.8rem]">Nuestra Mision</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 mb-0 text-[0.98rem] leading-[1.7] text-slate-500 sm:text-[1.05rem]">
          Brindar tranquilidad y seguridad a los conductores a traves de una ingenieria automotriz de excelencia, con rigor profesional, actualizacion cientifica constante y honestidad tecnica.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[2rem] bg-[#fffafb] p-5 sm:p-6">
        <span class="mb-5 grid size-12 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[#fff0f1] text-nasa-accent">
          <svg class="size-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2 12s3.5-6 10-6 10 6 10 6-3.5 6-10 6-10-6-10-6z" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.5" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="m-0 text-[1.45rem] font-bold tracking-[-0.05em] text-nasa-text sm:text-[1.8rem]">Nuestra Vision</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 mb-0 text-[0.98rem] leading-[1.7] text-slate-500 sm:text-[1.05rem]">
          Para el 2030, ser el laboratorio automotriz lider en innovacion y tecnologia, reconocidos por transformar el mantenimiento vehicular en una experiencia de precision integral.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
